So, we add 10 and 11 to get 21.  

But hold on, the question asks for the number *after* that one!

So, we add 11 and 21 to get 32.

But wait, the question asks for the number *after* that one!

So, we add 21 and 32 to get  \begin{align*}
\boxed{53}
